 at:29/04/2008 shift:($dx, 4) text:"[[Grand Theft Auto IV|GTA IV]]"
 at:17/02/2009 shift:($dx, -8) text:"[[Grand Theft Auto IV: The Lost and Damned|The Lost and Damned]]"
